ROME:

        Hold down the 'ALT' key and type any of the following numbers:

                                  (HERCULANEUM)

            "764"______________________Starts thunder and lightning.
            "826"__________________________Starts volcano exploding.
            "293"___________________________________Give host money.
            "119"____________________________________Give host toga.
            "275"________________________________Force ship to dock.
            "472"_________________________________________Win level.

